drag the chain
Homonym Number:
Word Class:phrase
Sense Number:
Definition:to be slow or behindhand in any group or competitive activity.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: (mainly shearers and drinkers)
